description:
He makes every mic a boom mic!

BOOMBOX 1: POP/STARZ includes the K/DA Ziggs Skin and the following three songs/levels for Hextech Mayhem: A League of Legends Story:

K/DA - POP/STARS (ft. Madison Beer, (G)I-DLE, Jaira Burns, League of Legends)
K/DA - MORE (ft. Madison Beer, (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, Seraphine, League of Legends)
K/DA - THE BADDEST (ft. (G)I-DLE, Bea Miller, Wolftyla, League of Legends)
